Class Phone

java.lang.Object
  com.nokia.midp.examples.xmlparser.Phone
public class Phone
extends java.lang.Object

The Phone class creates an Phone object. The object can have three Strings as features. Strings are: name, midpver and size, meaning phone model, MIDP version and screen size.
